meta.title: C++ class
meta.description: Creates a C++ header and source file  for a new class that you can add to a C++ project.

meta.title: QML file

meta.title: Qt Widgets Designer UI form
meta.description: Creates a Qt Widgets Designer form  that you can add to a Qt Widgets application project. This is useful if you already have an existing class for the UI business logic.
